Articles.Content: I installed real solar system to ksp and have a variety of other mods installed. It seems as if the texture file for Earth has not loaded onto kerbin but the height map has. I checked the RSS Textures folder and the files are in there, I have not checked if this is the case on any other planet or moon. Please help me with this problem, thank you.

Welcome to the forums! As this is a support request for a modded install, moved to that forum.

Can you follow the directions [here](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/92229-How-To-Get-Support-%28READ-FIRST%29) and post the correct log? That'll let me figure out what's wrong.
Ok, sorry if i posted this in the wrong spot I'm new to this fourm.
No problem! Also, so you know, new users' first few posts are moderated, so it may take a bit of time for them to show up (a moderator has to approve them).
